<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Frequently Asked Questions</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .faq h2 {
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .faq p {
            display: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0 10px 10px 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="faq">
        <h2>What services do you offer?</h2>
        <p>We offer a variety of pet grooming services including shampoo and blow dry, paw cleaning, oral care, and fur cutting.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq">
        <h2>How can I book an appointment?</h2>
        <p>You can book an appointment directly from our website by clicking the "Book Appointment" button next to the desired service.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq">
        <h2>What are your working hours?</h2>
        <p>Our working hours are from 9:00 AM to 6:00 PM, Monday to Saturday.</p>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Add event listeners to toggle content visibility
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
            const faqHeaders = document.querySelectorAll('.faq h2');
            faqHeaders.forEach(item => {
                item.addEventListener('click', function () {
                    const content = item.nextElementSibling;
                    if (content.style.display === "block") {
                        content.style.display = "none";
                    } else {
                        content.style.display = "block";
                    }
                });
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
